Teresa Giudice, Jeannie & Mama Mai, La Toya Jackson 310 (TV-PG)

In the Season 3 finale, "The Real Housewives of New Jersey" star Teresa Giudice struggles to hold it together as Tyler connects to her recently deceased mother. Tyler uncovers a treasure trove of family secrets via messages from the grave as he sits down with "The Real" star Jeannie Mai and the woman who's been keeping them - Jeannie's mother. Pop music legend La Toya Jackson finally finds the closure she's been looking for as Tyler answers the question all of America is asking: "What were Michael's final thoughts before he died?"
